<TITLE>Gerriets doubles up for reverberation adjustment</TITLE>
<TEXT>The G-sorber system comprises two layers of Trevira CS wide width fabric that Gerriets states will provide added flexibility and adaptability when controlling the acoustics within a room. The fabric is especially designed for the G-sorber, which is available in a variety of sizes up to 4m wide x 10m high. 
 
The absorption unit is designed to adjust the reverberation times for any genre of music, and to fit in with any style of dcor, can be ordered to a specific customised colour or digital print design. With its double layer textile design, G-sorber is a single roller unit with compact housing dimensions of 400mm x 448mm. It can be wall or ceiling mounted and is described as requiring little maintenance. 
 
www.gerriets.com</TEXT>
